                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">作者其余几本书的拼凑，卖的还是雪珥的视角。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="727417159">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-727417159" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-727417159" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="727417159">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/bayernwin/">geniuschow</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar10 rating" title="很差"></span>
                    <span>2013-09-19</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">不值一读。吹捧恭亲王倒还罢了，连醇亲王也要捧上一记；结构散乱，历史照片乱打水印，好在我是借的。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="747602403">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-747602403" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-747602403" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="747602403">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/boonup/">boonup</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-01-20</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">雪珥观点一向不附庸于传统史书，耳目一新。可能因为因为是海外学者的关系，海外史料的内容也比较殷实。文字不生硬，图文并茂。总之，读起来很流畅。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="778126011">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-778126011" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-778126011" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="778126011">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1919906/">紫极仙翁</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-02-17</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">恭亲王奕䜣，一个长期被传统史学界误读的人物，正如他那座位于后海边的府邸，更多人去恭王府，不是去凭悼恭亲王，而是去欣赏和珅。大清国主政的总理，晚清“改革开放”——洋务运动的总设计师，低调而默默无闻，甚至被人误解为窝囊。忧谗畏讥，这正是晚清以来民国、共和国总理的鲜明写照。理解了恭王的艰难，也就理解了改革的艰难，更理解了现实首辅的困境。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="605747100">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-605747100" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-605747100" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="605747100">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2204943/">顾小明</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2013-04-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">自《1909》后这是我读的他第二本书，和第一本一样总归还是带来了惊喜，可惜史料都不知道哪儿考出来的，总让我觉得我是在读八卦</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

